ğŸŒŸ Project Overview

This project predicts an individual's overall health and fitness status using machine learning and predictive analytics. It leverages health and lifestyle data to:

Analyze health patterns with EDA (Exploratory Data Analysis)

Train multiple machine learning models

Determine the best-performing model

Enable users to predict personal health & fitness through an interactive menu

The goal is to provide a data-driven tool to monitor health and help make informed lifestyle decisions.

ğŸ“Š Features
Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)

Visualize overall health condition distribution

Analyze stress levels vs. health condition

Correlation heatmap of numeric variables
Machine Learning Models

Logistic Regression

K-Nearest Neighbors (KNN)

Decision Tree (with pruned tree visualization)

Random Forest (primary model for prediction)

Predictive Analytics

Predict Healthy / Not Healthy based on user inputs

Calculates BMI automatically

Provides probability-based predictions

Model Evaluation

Accuracy score and confusion matrix for each model

Bar chart comparison to determine the best-performing model

