File: Health_Fitness_Expanded_5000_CORRECT.csv

Contents: 5000 records with features such as age, weight, height, BMI, sleep hours, stress level, alcohol & smoking habits, exercise routine, and self-rated overall health

Target: Binary_Health â€“ 1 for healthy, 0 for not healthy

